WEBVTT

00:01:27.628 --> 00:01:31.079
Now, they sure do
a lot of good stuff for us.

00:01:31.714 --> 00:01:34.355
And our family farmers
are great, we'd all agree.

00:01:34.379 --> 00:01:36.291
However,

00:01:36.315 --> 00:01:38.759
the trends in agriculture today are dire.

00:01:38.783 --> 00:01:40.664
The average age of a farmer in America,

00:01:40.688 --> 00:01:43.410
according to the latest
agricultural census --

00:01:43.434 --> 00:01:44.934
58.3.

00:01:44.958 --> 00:01:46.886
Of all the farmers,

00:01:46.910 --> 00:01:49.369
33 percent are 65 plus.

00:01:49.393 --> 00:01:51.379
That's a little caricature of my grandpa.

00:01:51.403 --> 00:01:52.727
(Laughter)

00:01:52.751 --> 00:01:54.348
He's still farming,

00:01:54.372 --> 00:01:56.506
and he's much older than 65.

00:01:56.530 --> 00:01:58.007
But to put that in perspective,

